title: Rainbow Six - BlackOps
description:
This is Rainbow Six: Black Ops, all Rainbow Six titles into one game!     ||
 Now you can play all seven Rainbow Six parts with one engine!:            ||
 * Tom Clancy's Rainbow Six (1998)                                         ||
 * Tom Clancy's Rainbow Six: Eagle Watch Expansion pack (1999)             ||
 * Tom Clancy's Rainbow Six: Rogue Spear (1999)                            ||
 * Tom Clancy's Rainbow Six: Rogue Spear: Urban Operations (2000)          ||
 * Tom Clancy's Rainbow Six: Covert Ops Essentials (2000)                  ||
 * Tom Clancy's Rainbow Six: Black Thorn (2001)                            ||
 * Tom Clancy's Rainbow Six: Take Down: Missions in Korea (2001)           ||
